<div id="review_3647622210" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3647622210" />
    <a title="Lisa" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/8051792-lisa"><img alt="Lisa" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1544530609p2/8051792.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3647622210?book_show_action=true">Nov 16, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Lisa" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Lisa" href="/user/show/8051792-lisa">Lisa</a>
      </span>

          marked it as unable-to-finish




        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3647622210" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer274608801669983733">As much as I have enjoyed Graham Greene recently, this one (his purported masterpiece) is not for me - abandoned at page 60. It is possible I&apos;ll pick it up again, but unlikely. Religion - Catholicism - is too much of a focus.</span>
  <span id="freeText274608801669983733" style="display:none">As much as I have enjoyed Graham Greene recently, this one (his purported masterpiece) is not for me - abandoned at page 60. It is possible I'll pick it up again, but unlikely. Religion - Catholicism - is too much of a focus.</span>
  <a data-text-id="274608801669983733" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


